msgctxt "768_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "That's not a bad idea. It would stand out when I'm playing my guitar or holding a mic."
msgstr "No es mala. Destacaría bastante ya que uso la guitarra o el micrófono."

msgctxt "780_Kiryu"
msgid "Do you know what kind of tattoo you want?"
